Package: openaps-ecu-zb
Version: __OPENAPS_VERSION__
Architecture: armv7ahf-vfp-neon
Maintainer: OpenAPS <bdbruin@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: openaps-base, openaps-inv-driver
Description: OpenAPS ecu-zb — ZigBee modem proxy and bus manager.
 Installs /home/applications/ecu-zb/ecu-zb and its /etc/rcS.d/S53 BusyBox
 init script. Drives the CC2530 modem on /dev/ttyO2 and proxies the
 802.15.4 link for inv-driver.
